<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635819>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–12. Guimaraesiella (Cicchinella) corrugata n. sp. 3, male head, dorsal and ventral views. 4, male genitalia, dorsal view. 5, male paramere, dorsal view. 6, male paramere, ventral view. 7, male mesosome, ventral view. (Figs 3–7 taken from Dinghushan specimens). 8, male paramere, dorsal view 9, male paramere, ventral view. 10, male mesosome, dorsal view. 11, male mesosome, ventral view (Figs 8–11 taken from Dadongshan specimens). 12, female subgenital plate and vulval margin, ventral view. Figures 4–12 to same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635819/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635815>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–2. Guimaraesiella (Cicchinella) corrugata n. sp. 1, male habitus, dorsal and ventral views. 2, female habitus, dorsal and ventral views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635815/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

